( b ) Makawana a Bahebera a a neng a le kwa Babelona a ne a bontsha jang gore a ineetse ka botlalo mo go Jehofa ?
Fa re batla go ineela ka botlalo mo go Jehofa , ke eng se re tshwanetseng go se tila ?
Ke eng se re ka simololang go se rata go feta tsela e re ratang Jehofa ka yone ?
Ke eng fa Paulo a ne a gakolola Bakeresete gore Modimo ke “ Jehofa a le mongwe fela ” ?
16 , 17 . ( a ) Ke boporofeti bofe jo bo diragadiwang mo metlheng ya rona , mme go nnile le diphelelo dife ?
( b ) Ke eng se se ka nnang sa senya kutlwano ya rona ?
18 , 19 . ( a ) Ke kgakololo efe e e mo go Baefeso 4 : 1 - 3 ?
( b ) Ke eng se re ka se dirang go thusa gore go nne le kutlwano mo phuthegong ?
Re ka bontsha jang gore re tlhaloganya gore “ Jehofa Modimo wa rona ke Jehofa a le mongwe fela ” ?
Go na le metse e mentsi ya batshwaraditlhapi gaufi le lotshitshi lwa Trinidad le lwa Tobago .
Gantsi Basupi ba ga Jehofa ba bua le batshwaraditlhapi ba ba kopanang le bone
PINA : 121 , 75
Ke eng fa phuthego ya Modimo e tlhomologile thata jaana ?
Baebele e bontsha jang gore re baleofi ?
Re tshwanetse go leba jang diphoso tsa rona le tsa batho ba bangwe ?
Baebele e ile ya bolelela pele jang koketsego ya batho ba ga Jehofa ?
Batlhanka ba ga Jehofa ba ile ba bontsha jang gore ba a ratana ?
( Bala Mika 4 : 1 , 3 . )
Seno se ile sa ba thusa gore ba nne ba le “ phepa mo mading a batho botlhe . ” — Ditiro 20 : 26 .
Ke eng fa koketsego ya batho ba ga Jehofa e tlhomologile thata jaana ?
Ke eng fa ba bangwe ba re utlwisa botlhoko ka dinako tse dingwe ?
( Bala Baroma 5 : 12 , 19 . )
Fa o ne o tshela kwa Iseraele ka nako ya ga Eli le bomorwawe , o ne o tla tsiboga jang ?
Dafide o ne a dira maleo afe a a masisi , mme Modimo o ne a dira eng ?
( a ) Moaposetoloi Petere o ne a palelwa jang ke go dira se a neng a se solofeditse ?
( b ) Fa Petere a sena go dira phoso , ke eng fa Jehofa a ile a tswelela pele a mo dirisa ?
Jesu o ne a tlhaloganya eng ka phoso ya ga Judase Isekariota le ya ga Petere ?
Baebele e ile ya bolelela pele gore batho ba ga Jehofa ba tla dira eng mo metlheng eno ya rona ?
Re tshwanetse go leba jang diphoso tsa ba bangwe ?
13 , 14 . ( a ) Ke eng fa re tshwanetse go itshokelana ?
( b ) Ke tsholofetso efe e re batlang go nna re e gopotse ?
Jesu o ne a re re tshwanetse go dira eng fa mongwe a re diretse phoso ?
Josefa o re tlhometse sekao sefe se se molemo ?
O tshwanetse go dira eng fa ba bangwe ba go diretse diphoso ?
( Bala Mathaio 5 : 23 , 24 . )
A go ikanyega ga bone e ne e le ga lefela ?
Re kgona go bona seo mo tseleng e Baebele e buang ka yone ka temogo le botlhale .
Diane 3 : 13 - 15 ya re : “ Go itumela motho yo o boneng botlhale , le motho yo o nnang le temogo , gonne go nna le jone e le papadi go botoka go na le go nna le selefera e le papadi mme go nna le jone e le kungo go botoka go na le gouta ka boyone .
Bo tlhwatlhwakgolo go feta dikorale , mme dilo tse dingwe tsotlhe tse di go itumedisang ga di ka ke tsa lekanngwa le jone . ”
Mme Jehofa o ikutlwa jang ka boikanyegi ?
E re ka ke ne ke le motsamaisimogolo , go ne go lebeletswe gore ke ntshe pipamolomo gore motlhatlhobi wa tsa lekgetho a tlodise matlho boferefere jo bo neng bo dirwa mo khampaning .
Seo se ile sa dira gore ke itsiwe ke le motho yo o sa ikanyegeng .
Ke tlhomela bomorwaake ba babedi sekao se se molemo e bile ke kgonne go tshwanelegela go newa ditshiamelo mo phuthegong .
Batlhatlhobi ba lekgetho mmogo le batho ba bangwe ba ke gwebisanang le bone , ba nkitse ke le motho yo o ikanyegang . ”
Ruthe o ne a fudugela kwa Iseraele kwa a neng a ka kgona go obamela Modimo wa boammaaruri gone .
